      <bioghist id="aspace_a8af9aebddaef21d6a449400286fca28">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Scroll and Key (incorporated as the Kingsley Trust Association) is a Yale senior society founded in 1841.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_143d89e5711db0e45831c134f3a72f69">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence among members of Scroll and Key, photographs, and a certificate honoring the 100th birthday of Howard Phipps, Yale Class of 1912.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
